<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">الخامسة:</span> قولهم: <span class="c3">{إِنَّا إِلَى رَبِّنَا مُنْقلِبُونَ}</span> ١.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">السادسة:</span> قولهم: <span class="c3">{وَمَا تَنْقِمُ مِنَّا}</span> إلى آخره.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">السابعة:</span> سؤالهم الله هذه المسألة.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الثامنة:</span> كلام الملأ له.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">التاسعة:</span> جوابه لهم.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
